parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Delayed or Unavailable Takata Airbag Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of Takata airbag recall repairs can lead to a significant risk of injury or death due to the potential for airbag malfunction.
symptoms: Owners receive notification of the recall but are unable to schedule repairs due to unavailable parts
are given conflicting information by dealerships
or experience long wait times for repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Failure to Notify Owners of Takata Airbag Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to notify owners of the Takata airbag recall can lead to a significant risk of injury or death due to the potential for airbag malfunction.
symptoms: Owners are not notified of the recall despite living at the same address for an extended period
and only discover the recall through other means.
